<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-1024x576.jpg" alt="Doctor with a patient" class="wp-image-407780" srcset="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-300x169.jpg 300w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-768x432.jpg 768w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/11/doctor-patient-shutterstock_126153410-16-x-9-2048x1152.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Shutterstock</figcaption></figure>



<p>Eight eligible <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/about-mayo-clinic" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mayo Clinic</a> hospitals earned A grades from&nbsp;<a href="https://nam12.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leapfroggroup.org%2F&amp;data=05%7C01%7Clea.dan%40mayo.edu%7Ce9b1511dbd64401f8efa08dac7fac64c%7Ca25fff9c3f634fb29a8ad9bdd0321f9a%7C0%7C0%7C638042177219464262%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=7SE6Xv0d1MmAEt%2FcayEnYIrmYt4j6Zaba7mvAjgjsj8%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">The Leapfrog Group</a>, an independent national nonprofit organization that provides safety ratings.</p>



<p>All eight hospitals have maintained straight A’s since spring 2022. Notably, <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/patient-visitor-guide/arizona" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mayo Clinic in Arizona</a> is among just 11 hospitals in the nation that have achieved an A in every Leapfrog grading cycle since 2012 — earning an all-time Straight A distinction from <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-hospitals-earn-highest-grades-for-patient-safety-from-leapfrog-group/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Leapfrog</a>. The ratings are intended to help patients choose their preferred healthcare destinations.</p>



<p>"Dr. Charlie Mayo once said that teamwork&nbsp;—&nbsp;with each member doing their part in the spirit of cooperation&nbsp;—&nbsp;is what makes great medicine possible. These grades reflect that same spirit: teams working together to make safe, high-quality care our constant standard," says&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/biographies/dowdy-sean-c-m-d/bio-20054619" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Sean Dowdy, M.D.</a>, Mayo Clinic's chief value officer.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Hospitals that received an A grade are:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Mayo Clinic in Arizona.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic in Florida.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic in Rochester.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic Health System in Albert Lea and Austin, Minnesota.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic Health System in Eau Claire, Wisconsin.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic Health System in Fairmont, Minnesota.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic Health System in La Crosse, Wisconsin.</li>



<li>Mayo Clinic Health System in Mankato, Minnesota.</li>
</ul>



<p>Mayo Clinic Health System in Red Wing, Minnesota, received a B grade.</p>



<p>The Leapfrog Group's Hospital Safety Grades are updated and published twice each year. The grade is based on 22 measures of publicly available hospital safety data and self-reported survey answers, which are combined to produce a single safety grade. A panel of patient safety experts developed the measures for the grade.</p>



<p>Many agencies rate quality in healthcare. Mayo Clinic is the only healthcare organization that consistently ranks among the top providers nationwide, regardless of the quality measure used.</p>
