					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->DEAR MAYO CLINIC:&nbsp;I love the fall, but I dread the shorter days and how I feel. I've read about seasonal affective disorder, but could you please tell me more about it? ANSWER:&nbsp;Seasonal affective disorder, or&nbsp;SAD, is a type of depression that's related to the changes in seasons. Symptoms typically appear in the fall, worsen through […]<p></p>
